03:14.542 --> 03:16.060
(applauding)

03:16.144 --> 03:17.544
(Quinn laughs)

03:17.595 --> 03:19.763
Here's a lesson for
your board, Mr. Shue.

03:19.848 --> 03:22.649
Don't text and drive. Ever.

03:22.717 --> 03:24.318
It's the stupidest thing
I've ever done.

03:24.385 --> 03:25.769
Besides sleeping with Puck.

03:25.854 --> 03:27.855
(quiet laughter)

03:27.906 --> 03:30.107
There's a lot of rumors floating
around, so let's clear the air.

03:30.225 --> 03:32.776
First of all, all my plumbing
still works, which is awesome.

03:32.861 --> 03:35.529
But my spine was severely
compressed in the car accident,

03:35.580 --> 03:38.732
which basically means
I can't move my feet or legs.

03:38.783 --> 03:40.066
But the good thing is that

03:40.118 --> 03:41.902
I'm starting to regain feeling,

03:41.953 --> 03:45.539
so with a lot of physical
therapy, and your prayers,

03:45.590 --> 03:47.257
I stand a good chance
for a full recovery.

03:47.342 --> 03:49.176
So no tears.

03:49.243 --> 03:51.745
That means you, Tina.

03:51.796 --> 03:53.764
Oh, and I apologize
for the number.

03:53.848 --> 03:56.183
My dance moves aren't
as smooth as Artie's yet.

03:56.250 --> 03:57.935
With practice,
they will be.

04:01.589 --> 04:05.592
I promise that by the time
we go to Nationals,

04:05.643 --> 04:07.694
I'll be out of this chair,

04:07.762 --> 04:09.747
and dancing on that stage.

04:09.814 --> 04:10.697
All right.

04:12.066 --> 04:13.784
Whoo!

